| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1480 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5ddcef8f-aa05-546b-a54f-c1dae71e7e9b"
